---
import AppLayout from "@/layouts/AppLayout.astro";
import { AuthScreen } from "@/features/auth/AuthScreen";
---

<AppLayout title="Entrar | TodoList">
  <main class="auth-shell">
    <section class="auth-aside">
      <div class="auth-aside__badge">TodoList</div>
      <h2>Trabalho enxuto, prioridade visivel, menos atrito no dia.</h2>
      <p>
        Um painel simples para organizar tarefas pessoais sem abrir mao de boa estrutura, autenticacao
        e consistencia visual.
      </p>
    </section>
    <AuthScreen client:load mode="login" />
  </main>
</AppLayout>
